              },
              "free_text": [
                " To 2.14 MeV level.",
                " The efficiency of the counting system could not be",
                " determined directly with any great accuracy, so the",
                " yield of the 2.14 MeV gamma-ray was used as a measure",
                " of the efficiency. The cross-section for producing",
                " the mirror state in 11C in the mirror reaction",
                " 12C(p,pn) has been found to be 2.8+-0.4 mb; the",
                " cross-section for producing the 11B state in the",
                " 12C(n,np) reaction should be the same."
              ]
            }
          ],
